-> BENEFITS OF SPRING DATA REPOSITORIES:

• They provide a better way to interact with database as there is no need to write the boilerplate code for CRUD operations.
• Pagination and Sorting are built-in methods simplifying handling of large datasets.
• Custom query can be written easily using @Query annotation.
• It has integration with other Spring Modules such Spring Security, Spring AOP.
• We can write queries based on methods, so there is no need to write SQL.

